Enter the name of the customer:gnana
Enter the number of blackdates:1
Enter the number of sunflower oil:2
Enter the number of soaps:5
Enter the number of detergents:6
Enter the number of sugar packets:1
customer phone number 8125814356
customer name gnana
tax= 2057.0
bill= 1870
